http://www.atr.org:80/discovery/pritchard.html 204.71.237.87 19970210003221 text/html 8632
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 10-Feb-97 00:33:09 GMT
Last-modified: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 08:33:55 GMT
