    <LI><A HREF="/townhall/columnists/duplantier/dupl052996.html"> 
        Duplantier: WELFARE REFORM/MI & MA -- 5/29/96</A>
    <LI><A HREF="/townhall/columnists/duplantier/dupl053096.html"> 
        Duplantier: WELFARE REFORM/IN, WI, CO -- 5/30/96</A>
    <LI><A HREF="/townhall/columnists/duplantier/dupl053196.html"> 
        Duplantier: WELFARE REFORM/WA -- 5/31/96</A>
    <LI><A HREF="/townhall/columnists/duplantier/dupl060396.html"> 
        Duplantier: "McCARTHYISM" -- 6/03/96</A>
    <LI><A HREF="/townhall/columnists/duplantier/dupl060496.html"> 
        Duplantier: TRUTH ABOUT COMMUNISM -- 6/04/96</A>
    <LI><A HREF="/townhall/columnists/duplantier/dupl060596.html"> 
        Duplantier: THE REAL McCARTHY-- 6/05/96</A>
