<head>
<TITLE>The Heritage Foundation Commentary -- Heritage </TITLE>
</head>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/heritage/paperh.jpg">
<blockquote>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="/heritage/commentary/commentary.gif" WIDTH=425 HEIGHT=100 BORDER=0 ALT="Commentary banner">
</CENTER>
<BR>
<b><i>The latest commentary and op-eds from Heritage President <a href="/heritage/staff/feulner.html">Dr. Edwin J. Feulner, Jr.</a> and Heritage analysts</b></i><br>

<HR SIZE=3 WIDTH=50%>
<p>
