http://www.atr.org:80/wash_times/fields.8-11.html 204.71.237.87 19970210004914 text/html 5569
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 10-Feb-97 00:50:02 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 05-Aug-96 13:50:34 GMT
