<DOCOLDNO>IA035-000698-B025-128</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.atr.org:80/townhall/columnists/fumento/fume071896.html 204.71.237.87 19970210005429 text/html 6781
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 10-Feb-97 00:55:18 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 18-Jul-96 20:43:08 GMT
Content-length: 6596
