<DOC>
<DOCNO>WT20-B34-118</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA035-000698-B025-401</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.atr.org:80/townhall/columnists/howley/howl030896.html 204.71.237.87 19970210005621 text/html 6808
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
