<html>

<head>
<title>Columnist Karen Kerrigan</title>
</head>


<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/townhall/background.jpg">

<center>




<h2>Town Hall Guest Columnist<p>
Karen Kerrigan</h2>


</center>


<h5><a href="/townhall/columnists/i-kerrigan.html.cgi">[Graphics On]</a></h5>
<hr size="3" width="60%">








<p>

<img src="/sbsc/kerrigan.jpg" align="left" 
vspace="25" hspace="8" alt="Photo of Karen Kerrigan">

<a href="/sbsc/kerrigan.html"><b>Biography</b></a>
<UL>
<li>January 31, 1996 <a href="/sbsc/sbb21.html">Small Business Agenda Faces An Uphill Battle</a>
<li>December 1995 <a href="/sbsc/br-1295a.html">Rhetoric Throttles Aid for Small Businesses</a>
<li>December 1995 <a href="/sbsc/br-1295.html">Balanced Budget Means Bottom-Line Gains</a>
