<DOCNO>WT20-B34-142</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA035-000698-B027-3</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.atr.org:80/wash_times/pruden.7-14.html 204.71.237.87 19970210010142 text/html 5429
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 10-Feb-97 01:02:30 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 08-Jul-96 16:15:17 GMT
Content-length: 5246
