<DOCOLDNO>IA035-000698-B027-26</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.atr.org:80/wash_times/pruden.7-7.html 204.71.237.87 19970210010154 text/html 5532
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 10-Feb-97 01:02:42 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 02-Jul-96 14:26:26 GMT
