<html>

<head>
<title>Columnist Phyllis Schlafly</title>
</head>


<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/townhall/background.jpg">

<center>




<h2>Town Hall Guest Columnist<p>
Phyllis Schlafly</h2>


</center>


<h5><a href="/townhall/columnists/i-schlafly.html.cgi">[Graphics On]</a></h5>
<hr size="3" width="60%">








<p>






<a href="/townhall/columnists/schlafly.html"><b>Biography</b></a>
<UL>
