<html><head><title>Agencia Interamericana de Prensa Economica - Columns</title></head>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/townhall/background.jpg">

<center><h2>Agencia Interamericana de Prensa Economica</h2></center>
<blockquote>
Agencia Interamericana de Prensa Economica (AIPE) was established in 1991 to serve Spanish-language newspapers and magazines in the United States, Latin America and Spain with economic newsfeatures and op-eds.  Some 36 publications in 15 countries currently subscribe to AIPE; their aggregate circulation is over three million.  So far 269 different authors have written for AIPE.  Its columnists and stringers from the US and main Latin American capitals comment each week on the most important economic and political issues of the day.<p>

<center><a href="mailto:Ball.AIPE@worldnet.att.net">For information, please contact Carlos A. Ball, Editor and Publisher.</a><p>


</blockquote>
<P> <br><center>
