<li>3/11/96 <a href="/heritage/library/categories/budgettax/bg1071.html">Clinton's FY 1997 Budget: The Era of Big Government Lives On</a> by <a href="/heritage/staff/hodge.htm">Scott A. Hodge</a>. (Backgrounder #1071)
<li>7/1/95 <a href="/heritage/library/categories/healthwel/prbeard.html">Minimum Wage
 Millionaires: The Capitalist Way To Save Social Security</a> by Sam Beard. (Summer 1995 Policy Review)
<li>3/9/92 <a href="http://www.townhall.com/heritage/library/categories/budgettax/ib171.html">The Higher Education Act: Another Middle-Class Entitlement</a> by Angela Hulsey. (Issues Bulletin No. 171)


<li>See also <a href="/heritage/library/index/i2.html">Medicare</a> and <a href="/heritage/library/index/i4.html">Social Security</a>.
