<li>3/1/96 <a href="/heritage/p_review/mar96/brown.html">A New Contract with America</a> by Sam Brownback.  (March-April 1996 Policy Review: The Journal of American Citizenship)


<li>1/29/96 <a href="/heritage/library/categories/crimelaw/lect553.html">Ending Judicial Dictatorship</a> by Patrick J. Buchanan. (Lecture #553)
<li>1/1/96 <a href="/heritage/p_review/jan96/preserv.html">Preserve, Protect, and Defend</a> A Symposium.  (January-February 1996 Policy Review: The Journal of American Citizenship)


<li>10/18/95 <a href="/heritage/library/categories/crimelaw/bg1057.html">Why the Legal Services Corporation Must Be Abolished</a> by Kenneth F. Boehm and Peter T. Flaherty. (Backgrounder #1057)
<li>10/1/95 <a href="/heritage/library/categories/crimelaw/flah.html">Legal Disservices Corp.: There Are Better Ways To Provide Legal Aid to The Poor</a> by Kenneth F. Boehm and Peter T. Flaherty. (Fall 1995 Policy Review)
