Articles from <a href="i-ac.html"><i>American Civilization</i></a> or transcripts from <a href="i-renew.html">"Renewing American Civilization"</a> will come up in your search, or can be accessed via their index pages by following the appropriate link above.<P>

<big>Note:</big> This search engine is compiled by Town Hall, so the results page you receive will not have the standard PFF look to it, but it <b>will</b> link you to our documents. If you choose to "Narrow Search," you will be fed into the Town Hall general search engine, and will need to specify "PFF Only" if you want to search only our documents.  <br>
Also, some of the documents you pull up through the search engine may not have been converted to our new look just yet, so please bear with us as we continue to improve our pages. <b>Thanks!</b><P>

