<HEAD>

<TITLE>The Big Change -- PFF</TITLE>

<META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="Internet Assistant for Word 1.0Z">
<META NAME="AUTHOR" CONTENT="Chris Pressley">
<META NAME="OPERATOR" CONTENT="Chris Pressley">
</HEAD>

<BODY BACKGROUND="backgrnd.gif" BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF"  LINK="#8C1717" VLINK="#545454" ALINK="#FF0000">
<map name="wst">
<area shape="rect" coords="0,0,92,20" href="#works">
<area shape="rect" coords="93,0,193,20" href="#speeches">
<area shape="rect" coords="194,0,318,20" href="#testimonies"></map>

<blockquote>

<a href="welcome.html"><img src="bi.gif" align="right" border="0" alt="PFF"></a>
<center>
<a href="wst.map"><img src="wst.gif" border="0" USEMAP="#wst" ISMAP></a>
<img src="bchead.gif" alt="Big Change">
</center>
<br><br><P>
<table>
<tr>
<td valign="top" width="20%">
America is undergoing a transformation as profound as the Industrial
Revolution.  Our work, leisure, education, warfare &#133; our
conceptions about society itself are all changing.  Revolution
is an over used word these days, but we are experiencing one.
Revolutions are messy; they often get violent, and unless we have
a sense of where we want to go we may end up in a place we don't
want to be.
<P>
Yet no one in the Imperial City wants to talk about Big Change.
 We are hampered by having lived most of our lives in a stable
political world where Revolution just didn't happened.  But it's
here, so now what?
<td valign="top">
<img src="bullet.gif" hspace="5" align="top"><a href="/pff/bigchange/vlah0228.html"><b>The Meaning of Revolution</a></b> by Michael Vlahos<br>
<img src="bullet.gif" hspace="5" align="top"><a href="/pff/bigchange/bytecity.html"><b>Byte City</b></a> by Michael Vlahos<br>
<img src="bullet.gif" hspace="5" align="top"><a href="/pff/bigchange/wrbtcity.html"><b>The War After Byte City</a></b> by Michael Vlahos<br>
<img src="bullet.gif" hspace="5" align="top"><a href="/pff/fofp.html"><b>The Future of Progress</a></b> by Jeffrey Eisenach<br>
<img src="bullet.gif" hspace="5" align="top"><a href="/pff/pff6.html"><b>From Virtuality to Reality</a></b> by Newt Gingrich<br>
<img src="bullet.gif" hspace="5" align="top"><a href="mv011896.html"><b>Are We Reliving the 1850s?</b></a> by Michael Vlahos<br>                               
<img src="bullet.gif" hspace="5" align="top"><a href="aspen-mv.html"><b>Message from Aspen</b></a> by Michael Vlahos                     <br>                                    
<img src="bullet.gif" hspace="5" align="top"><a href="vlahos_summit.html"><b>Surfing the Sheraton:</b></a>  A Report from the internet conference<br>                        
</tr>
</table>
</ul>
</blockquote>
<P><br><P>
<map name="footer">
<area shape="rect" coords="0,0,33,20" href="welcome.html">
