</blockquote><p>
Friedman, Milton. 1968.  "Regressive Income Tax."  <i>Newsweek</i> (April 22).  Reprinted in <i>An Economist's Protest</i>.  Glen Ridge, New Jersey: Thomas Horton, 1972, pp. 76-77.
