<HEAD>

<TITLE>Town Hall Spotlight: Elections & Governing Updates</TITLE>

</HEAD>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/townhall/paper2.jpg">  
<P>

<CENTER>
<img src="/townhall/spotlights/elections/spot.gif">
<br><H2>Elections & Governing Updates</CENTER></H2>

The 1996 campaigns are underway and Town Hall will be bringing you the latest information from the campaign trail.  Check here often for the latest poll numbers, press releases, and candidate information.
<i>
 If you are interested in having your information posted here, send your press release to <a href="mailto:jgarth@townhall.com">jgarth@townhall.com</a>. <b>Priority is given to documents already in HTML format.
</b></i>
<P>

<P>
<P>
<P>
<HR>
<P><a name="week"></a>
<center><h3>Check out Heritage's new <a href="/heritage/issues96/tblcon.html">Issues '96</a>! The Candidate's Briefing Book </h3><p>
<b>Do the polls really matter? View the latest Presidential and Senate race <a href="http://www.townhall.com/townhall/spotlights/elections/senate96.html">poll numbers</a> from around the country and decide for yourself.<p></b></center> 

<p>
<b>Campaign Connections</b>
<ul>

<li><b>Arizona</b>: 
